<p>The blonde replied: 'No, we're just friends and we're civil. He had a fun time. He was hooking up with multiple girls while we were on the Gold Coast!'</p>

<p>When asked if she was one of the 'multiple girls', Stacey reiterated they were merely friends.</p>

